{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778468456880,"sessionID":"ses_1eb095841ffeI7PjslP58h1Hev","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:38","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","content":"GO:0009095 has been obsoleted as requested. The term was a pre-composed superpathway (MetaCyc:PWY-3481) combining L-phenylalanine and L-tyrosine biosynthesis, which are already represented by separate GO terms. Annotations can be migrated to the consider terms GO:0009094 (L-phenylalanine biosynthetic process) or GO:0006571 (L-tyrosine biosynthetic process) as appropriate.\n\nChanges committed in PR #<NN>.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778468456871,"end":1778468456879}},"id":"prt_e14fb044a002Tw0lBWC8y9b0TY","sessionID":"ses_1eb095841ffeI7PjslP58h1Hev","messageID":"msg_e14fafb29001uPSToipm1Jtgjo"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778468464943,"sessionID":"ses_1eb095841ffeI7PjslP58h1Hev","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"functions.write:39","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","content":"Obsoletion of GO:0009095 aromatic amino acid biosynthetic process, prephenate pathway\n\n## Summary\nObsoleted GO:0009095 because it is a pre-composed term representing a MetaCyc superpathway that combines two separate pathways already represented in GO. This obsoletion follows the signal in the issue that the term should instead be represented as a GO-CAM model.\n\n## Changes made\n- Removed all logical axioms from GO:0009095 (is_a, intersection_of, synonyms, xref)\n- Prefixed name with \"obsolete\"\n- Prefixed definition with \"OBSOLETE.\"\n- Added comment explaining that the term represents a GO-CAM model\n- Added term_tracker_item linking to issue #32005\n- Added two `consider` tags pointing to candidate replacements:\n  - GO:0009094 ! L-phenylalanine biosynthetic process\n  - GO:0006571 ! L-tyrosine biosynthetic process\n\n## Checklist\n- [x] PLAN: The issue and all its context has been analyzed, the intent is clear, and a plan for addressing it has been created\n- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: Current state of the ontology validates prior to any changes\n- [x] TERM-SEARCH: Relevant ontology terms have been consulted; confirmed no other terms reference GO:0009095\n- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: term-obsoletion skill procedures followed\n- [x] EDITS: correct procedure followed (checkout -> edit in terms/ -> checkin)\n- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: all axioms removed from obsolete term; consider terms added appropriately\n- [x] METADATA: comment, term_tracker_item, is_obsolete, consider tags correctly formatted\n- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: robot convert and robot reason (ELK) both pass after edits\n- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: changes committed with detailed message\n\n## Issue context\n- Issue: https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/32005\n- Original reason for obsoletion: GO:0009095 is pre-composed and should be represented as a GO-CAM model (MetaCyc:PWY-3481 = superpathway of L-phenylalanine and L-tyrosine biosynthesis).\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/runner/work/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778468464938,"end":1778468464942}},"id":"prt_e14fb09a90019KCOfabxPEhVQ7","sessionID":"ses_1eb095841ffeI7PjslP58h1Hev","messageID":"msg_e14fafb29001uPSToipm1Jtgjo"}}
